{"tid":2433389,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：即使律政司就15人獲保釋上訴得直　被告亦有權再上訴","createTime":"2021-03-05T01:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T11:07:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22e34b45eefd94dac91e1b25c9c5ff64b20ed24f","tid":2433389,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"47名民主派人士被控「串謀顛覆國家政權」案，15人原本獲准保釋，但被律政司即時提出上訴而需繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊在一個電台節目表示，相關程序會在高等法院處理，即使律政司上訴得直，被告若認為法官引用錯誤法律原則，亦有權提出上訴，但要取得上訴庭或終審庭許可，又指今次案件爭議性較大，希望法庭盡早騰出時間處理。 <br />\n<br />\n至於為何只有15人獲准保釋，湯家驊指案件仍在司法程序當中，不宜有過多討論，但他相信法官會考慮，有無證據令他信服，被告不會再干犯危害國安的行為，會先確認這方面，再去考慮保釋條件。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381647&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUjX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=173c4c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381647</a>"},{"pid":"0b3d38b61192dc12e7418e69c3e9a79a8a209baf","tid":2433389,"uid":39167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"律政屍：本案件屬浪費公帑，因而取消上訴，無政治考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7fb4029119ae363eca48923339b3832b0463c2","tid":2433389,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:57:40.000Z","msg":"衰十一有冇得上訴？"},{"pid":"8cdb0ff12a4c625335e46b10b7891fa7a6debfaa","tid":2433389,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:58:19.000Z","msg":"好撚有法痔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90232afcb86648c68fad50bdbbe4bbb8702937e5","tid":2433389,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4ca080d092b7d9fce9930e2af240f30ce22924","tid":2433389,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0